Ah, oh!

00:41.040 --> 00:44.210
[heavy breathing]

00:44.277 --> 00:45.979
- Ah, Fee, can you tell me

00:46.045 --> 00:47.847
why we're following Foo around
like this?

00:47.914 --> 00:49.783
- Ssh, he's gonna hear us.

