18:43.188 --> 18:46.158
♪ What'll I do? ♪

18:46.225 --> 18:48.060
- ♪ What'll I do ♪

18:48.126 --> 18:52.397
♪ When I am wondering who ♪

18:52.464 --> 18:58.170
♪ Is punching you,
