- FEE: ♪ What'll I do ♪

18:59.972 --> 19:04.376
♪ With just a photograph ♪

19:04.443 --> 19:10.349
♪ To tell my troubles to? ♪

19:10.415 --> 19:13.719
- ♪ When I'm alone with only ♪

19:13.785 --> 19:16.522
♪ Dreams of you ♪

19:16.588 --> 19:22.194
♪ That won't come
