- ♪ What'll I do? ♪

19:25.297 --> 19:28.166
- ♪ What'll we do? ♪♪

19:32.971 --> 19:35.140
- This is stupid.

19:35.207 --> 19:36.608
- [crash]

19:36.675 --> 19:38.710
- Listen up, universe, I don't
understand what kind

19:38.777 --> 19:42.848
