me and my brother apart.

19:42.915 --> 19:44.650
But it ends now!

19:44.716 --> 19:46.118
You hear me?

19:46.184 --> 19:48.020
I'm gonna get my brother back.

19:48.086 --> 19:50.756
- [snores]
- Ah!

19:50.822 --> 19:52.958
- ♪

19:53.025 --> 19:55.594
- Wake up, Foo!

19:55.661 --> 19:57.162
- Ah!

19:57.229 --> 19:58.830
- Aaah!

19:58.897 --> 20:03.368
- ♪

20:03.435 --> 20:05.037
- Ah, what's going on?

20:05.103 --> 20:08.674
- I'm gonna break through
this stupid force field thing!

20:08.740 --> 20:13.845
- What...do
you...want...me to do?

20:13.912 --> 20:15.314
- FEE: Brace yourself!

20:20.085 --> 20:21.653
- It's not gonna work.

20:21.720 --> 20:23.622
- Yes, it will.

